 being shot while commanding at Fort Campbell|publisher=Leaf Chronicle|url=https://www.theleafchronicle.com/story/news/local/fort-campbell/2018/10/02/general-david-petreaus-fort-campbell-101st-airborne-division/1434072002/}}\n* {{Cite news|last=Reiss |first=Robert. |publication-date=October 2018 |year=2018 |title=The Leadership Issue|publisher=The CEO Forum|url=https://theceoforumgroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/leadership_whole_sm-compressed.pdf}}\n* {{cite news |last1=Petraeus |first1=David |last2=Whitehouse |first2=Sheldon |title=Putin and other authoritarians\u2019 corruption is a weapon \u2014 and a weakness |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/2019/03/08/putin-other-authoritarians-corruption-is-weapon-weakness/ |work=The Washington Post |date=March 8, 2019}}\n* {{cite news |title=David Petraeus Offers Big Ideas for Leadership, Foreign Policy |url=https://www.stitcher.com/podcast/cbs-radio-news/intelligence-matters/e/59514982 |work=Intelligence Matters |publisher=CBS News Radio |date=March 19, 2019}}\n* {{cite podcast |host=Guy Raz |title=General David Petraeus |website=Wisdom From the Top |publisher=Built-It Productions |date=21 May 2019 |url=https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/general-david-petraeus/id1460154838?i=1000438946682}}\n* {{cite podcast |title=General David Petraeus: The Perils of Victory |website=What It Takes |publisher=Academy of Achievement |date=3 June 2019 |url=https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/general-david-petraeus/id1460154838?i=1000438946682}}\n* {{cite news |last1=Petraeus |first1=David |last2=Serchuk |first2=Vance |title=Can America Trust the Taliban to Prevent Another 9/11?|url=https://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/afghanistan/2020-04-01/can-america-trust-taliban-prevent-another-911|work=Foreign Affairs|date=April 1, 2020}}\n{{refend}}\n\n===Academic and other works===\n{{refbegin|30em}}\n* {{Cite journal |last=Lorenz |first=G. C. |last2=Willbanks |first2=James H. |last3=Petraeus |first3=David H. |last4=Stuart |firs