76300 \"The Story of Power\"], Jon Meacham, ''Newsweek'', December 19, 2008.\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20090122111504/http://www.prospect-magazine.co.uk/article_details.php?id=10558 An Intellectual Surge], James Crabtree, ''Prospect Magazine'', January 17, 2009.\n* [https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/nation/thegamble/ The Generals' Insurgency: The Story Behind the U.S. Troop Surge in Iraq]. ''The Washington Post''.\n* [http://www.deseretnews.com/article/700019225/Gen-David-Petraeus-the-top-commander-in-the-Middle-East-comes-to-BYU.html \"Gen. David Petraeus, the top commander in the Middle East, comes to BYU\"], Sara Israelsen-Hartley, ''[[Deseret News]]'', March 25, 2010.\n* [https://www.vanityfair.com/politics/features/2010/05/petraeus-exclusive-201005 \"The Professor of War\"], Mark Bowden, ''Vanity Fair'', May 2010.\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20110404055916/http://www.prezydent.pl/archiwum/archiwum-aktualnosci/rok-2010/art%2C48%2C819%2Codznaczenie-generala-davida-petraeusa.html \"Odznaczenie genera\u0142a Davida Petraeusa\"] (in Polish) [https://web.archive.org/web/20110404055911/http://www.prezydent.pl/archiwum/archiwum-galerii/rok-2010/galeria%2C380.html (gallery)], President of the Republic of Poland, April 7, 2010, in Polish.\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20110425033602/http://www.wp.mil.pl/pl/artykul/8988 \"Gen. David Petraeus z wizyt\u0105 w Polsce\"] (in Polish) [https://web.archive.org/web/20110425093610/http://www.mon.gov.pl/pl/galeria/3403 (gallery)], Ministry of National Defence of the Republic of Poland, April 8, 2010, in Polish.\n* [http://www.oprah.com/ \"Words that Soothe, Ideas that Delight\"] contributor, General David H. Petraeus, ''[[O, The Oprah Magazine]]'', p.&nbsp;174, April 2011.\n* Dexter Filkins, \"General Principles\", ''The New Yorker'', December 17, 2012, pp.&nbsp;76\u201381.\n* [https://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/mar/06/pentagon-iraqi-torture-centres-link \"Revealed: Pentagon's link to Iraqi torture centres. Gene